\ref 0001
\ELANBegin 0.000
\ELANEnd 1.000
\ELANParticipant unknown
\tlt                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
\cm this recording contains excerpts from a longish negotiation process regarding belis ("pride price") - it was recorded in a stop and go fashion, i.e. while there are extended segements (>15 minutes) of continuous recording, tape has been stopped repeatedly since no further contributions were made has been collated from two different tapes, the first tape ends after ca. 30.30 minutes (with a brief segment without recording), everything that follows (> 60 minutes) is from the second tape the original transcript was segmented into 4 files which were worked on independently and at different times, hence there will be many inconsistencies across transcriptions and translations. Each transcription segment is also at a different stage of processing, as noted in a comment line at the beginning of each of them This segment was labled: MárioJaoa_belis5_wmmb_ad_01dec02_01 Belis Transkripsi Mb/ AT: English free translation, spell check of all free translations, additional interlinear.
\dt 29/Sep/2006                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 
